OL,3,CWhere will your tip go? New law stops
OL,4,Cbusinesses pocketing staff tips
OL,6,FTips must now be passed to employees
OL,7,Fby the end of the following month from
OL,8,Fwhen they were received.
OL,10,FIf an employer breaks the law and
OL,11,Fretains tips, a worker will be able to
OL,12,Fbring a claim to an employment
OL,13,Ftribunal.
OL,15,FHowever, hospitality industry bosses
OL,16,Fhave cautioned that the move could hit
OL,17,Funder-pressure businesses with an
OL,18,F"additional cost".
