OL,3,CWhere will your tip go? New law stops
OL,4,Cbusinesses pocketing staff tips
OL,6,FIt has said that distribution of these
OL,7,Ftips must be "fair", in line with a
OL,8,Fgovernment code of practice published
OL,9,Fearlier this year.
OL,11,FAgency workers will also be entitled
OL,12,Fto the tips as part of the rules.
OL,14,FThe change comes eight years after a
OL,15,Fgovernment report first suggested the
OL,16,Fpolicy could be introduced following a
OL,17,Freview.
