OL,6,FThe Department for Business and Trade
OL,7,Fpredicted that the new law will mean a
OL,8,Ffurther #200 million will be received
OL,9,Fby workers rather than their employers.
OL,11,FKate Nicholls, chief executive of
OL,12,Findustry body UKHospitality, said:
OL,13,F"The people working in hospitality are
OL,14,Fthe lifeblood of our sector and these
OL,15,Fchanges rightly ensure tips hard-
OL,16,Fearned through excellent service will
OL,17,Fend up entirely in their pockets.
