OL,6,F"We completely support the changes
OL,7,Fcoming into effect today, which will
OL,8,Fformalise what is already commonplace
OL,9,Fin the sector as businesses have been
OL,10,Fpreparing for this legislation for a
OL,11,Fnumber of years.
OL,13,F"New rules naturally come with an
OL,14,Fadministrative burden and businesses
OL,15,Fwill see some additional cost as they
OL,16,Fwork through them in practice.
